  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta Semme bija famai-\ntata Deewa Preekſchā / un ta\nSemme bija pilna Warras-Dar-\nba."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad redſeja DEews to\nSemmi/ un raugi/ ta bija famai-\ntata/ wiſſa Meeſa bij fauw Zettu\nfamaitajuſi wirs Semmes."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un DEews fazzija us\nNoii:wiſſoMeeſuGalsirr preekſch\nman nahzis/ jo ta Semme irr pil-\nna Warras- Darba zaur wiſ-\nneem/ un redſi/ es nomaitaschu\ntohs lihds ar to Semmi."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Darrajs few Schfirſtu no\nPreedas-Kohka/ ar Mahjokteem\nbuhs tew to Schfirſtu darriht/\nun tew buhs to apſwiſkeht no\nEekſch-un Ahra-puffes arDarwu."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tew buhs winnu ta\ndarriht / trihſſints Ohlekſchn lai\nirr ta Schfirſta Garrums/ peez-\ndefimits Ohlekſchu tas Plat-\ntums/ un trihsdefmits Ohlekſchu\nwinna Augstums."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Weenu Lohgu buhs tew\ntam Schfirſtain darriht / Ohlekſ\nLeeluma buhs tew to wirs-Gallá\npataitiht / un tahs Durwis buhs\ntew winna Sahnôs lift/tew buhs\nwinnu ar ( trium Behnixeem )\nappaſchajn / widdeju/ un wirfe-\njn darriht."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo redſi / Es atweddiſchu\nUhdens-Pluhdus wirs Semmes/\npar Nomattafchanu wiſſas Mee-\nfas/ eekſch ka dſihwa Dwascha irr\nappaſſch Debbes / wiſſain kas"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es uhszelschn Derribu\nar tew/ un tew buhs Schfirſti eet\nlihds ar taweem Dehleem / un ar\ntawn Seetwu / un tawo Dehlu\nSeewahn."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tew buhs no wiſſa/ kas\ndſihwo / no wiſſas Meeſas pa di-\nweem/ no wiſſa Schfirſta eeſest/\nka tee ar tewim dſihwi paleek/\nTehwainim un Mahtitei buhe\nteem buht."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No teem Putneem pehz\nfawas Kahrtas / un no teem Loh-\npeem pehz fawas Kahrtas/ un no\nwiſſeem Semmes Tahrpeem pehz\nfawas Kahrtas/ diwi no wiſſeem\nnahks pee tew / ka tee dſihwi pa-\nleek."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tu nemmees pee feiw\nno wiſſadas Barribas / ko ehſ\nwarr/ unsakrahji to pee feewis/ ko\nta tew un winneem par Barribu\neffoti."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Noiiſdarrija pehz wiſ-\nfeem/ ko DEews tam bij pawehle-\njis/ ta darrija wiſsch."
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
